The Doomsday Cult Couple Who Killed Their Babies And Exes To Go On Holiday

Chad Daybell and Lori Vallow shocked the world in 2019, after killing their exes and children and fleeing to get married and spend their honeymoon in Hawaii.

Now, Chad Daybell’s trial shocked again. New videos and police reports paint a really grim picture. This doomsday couple is simply the worst.

They left four people dead and took no responsibility for it.

Meanwhile, they acted high and mighty, claiming they spoke to God and could tell who was a good soul and who was an evil one. Except they did not look in the mirror.

Did karma finally catch up with them? What is the super recent verdict of Chad’s June 2024 trial? This is the sickening story of Chad Daybell and Lori Vallow.
